          <h3>
            <a href="../../login" class="favorite favorite_90"><span>*</span></a>
            
              <a href="../../proposals/90" class="title">Running without Systems Management Interrupts </a>
            
            
          </h3>

          <div class="excerpt">
            Describe the implementation, benefits and trade-offs of running without non-fatal System Management Interrupts in a Real-Time Enterprise level environment.  

          </div>
        </td>

        
        <td class='track block track-13'>
