          <h3>
            <a href="../../login" class="favorite favorite_27"><span>*</span></a>
            
              <a href="../../proposals/27" class="title">Power management: Communicating needs and desires</a>
            
            
          </h3>

          <div class="excerpt">
            Implementing power management is the job of the kernel - however, it's userspace's job to let it know what functionality is needed. What interfaces do we need to expose, and how should userspace be making use of them?
          </div>
        </td>

        
        <td class='track block track-11'>
          <a href="tracks/11">Kernel/Userspace/User  Interfaces</a>
        </td>
        

        
          <td class='date'>
            06/05/2009
